            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="11101474">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">有三層塔一所，未加莊嚴。

瓜按：本書既然如“洞房周匝”亦作箋注，此處“莊嚴”亦不妨顺手爲之。楊勇先生固然明了瞭，讀者未必知道此處“莊嚴”做何解。“莊嚴”者，装飾佛像也。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-02-03 15:53</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>有三層塔一所，未加莊嚴。</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>瓜按：本書既然如“洞房周匝”亦作箋注，此處“莊嚴”亦不妨顺手爲之。楊勇先生固然明了瞭，讀者未必知道此處“莊嚴”做何解。“莊嚴”者，装飾佛像也。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11101474/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2011-02-03 15:53
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
